This is an excellent strategic task. You're not asking for a simple redesign; you're asking to re-architect the entire psychological flow of the Lumina website using the proven 10-section conversion framework, while preserving the high-end brand identity I previously identified.

This new structure will take the same brand and content and map it to a journey explicitly designed to move a visitor from passive interest to an active lead by building emotional buy-in before providing logical justification.

Here is the complete, filled-in prompt template for the new, conversion-optimized Lumina Property Management homepage.

